results.title: New Orleans Love
results.description:
"NOLA Love," 2014, 24x48 inches, acrylic on canvas

"New Orleans Love" is another variation of New Orleans Rising: they are meant to be shown as a pair. This painting goes back to my love of the city and its laissez-faire, anything goes attitude. I painted an oak tree with Spanish moss, because one of my favorite things is New Orleans live Oak Tees. I think they are as good a symbol as any to describe a landscape describes Louisiana.
